{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WebRTC","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/WebRTC","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>WebRTC</strong> (<em>Web Real-Time Communication</em>) 是一个可以用在视频聊天，音频聊天或 P2P 文件分享等 Web App 中的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/API\">API</a>。</p>\n<p>WebRTC 主要由以下几个部分组成：</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"getusermedia\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getUserMedia\"><code>getUserMedia</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>为一个 RTC 连接获取设备的摄像头与 (或) 麦克风权限，并为此 RTC 连接接入设备的摄像头与 (或) 麦克风的信号。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"rtcpeerconnection\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection\"><code>RTCPeerConnection</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>用于配置音频或视频聊天。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"rtcdatachannel\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel\"><code>RTCDataChannel</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>用于设置两个浏览器之间的<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/P2P\">端到端 <small>(en-US)</small></a> 数据连接。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/WebRTC\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebRTC</a> on Wikipedia</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebRTC_API\">Guide to WebRTC on MDN</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/rtcpeerconnection\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Browser support of WebRTC</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"WebRTC (Web Real-Time Communication) 是一个可以用在视频聊天，音频聊天或 P2P 文件分享等 Web App 中的 API。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/webrtc","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/webrtc/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/WebRTC","title":"WebRTC"}],"pageTitle":"WebRTC - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}